owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An accommodation is a listing or property that is available to rent on a short-term basis on airbnb.com
An accommodation rating is the rating given to a property by a guest indicating their level of satisfaction.
An activity is a generic excursion that is available to do in Ireland.
The activity type classifies the activity into a category.
An amenity is a service available to a guest in an accommodation.
Country refers to the location where the counties are located.
Host is the owner of the accommodation that rents the property to guests.
Location is where the accommodation or activity is based.
PropertyType is the nature of the property, e.g. apartment, house, room.
Review is the comments a guest makes about the host or accommodation that is posted on Airbnb.
RoomType is the different types of rooms available to a guest.

rdf:Description.r2rml:sqlQuery: SELECT ACCOMMODATION.ACCOMMODATIONID as ACCOMMODATIONID, AMENITYJOIN.AMENITYID AS AMENITYIDJ, HOSTID,NAME,DESCRIPTION,LISTINGURL,NEIGHBORHOODOVERVIEW,ACCOMMODATES,LOCATION,BATHROOMS,BATHROOMSTEXT,BEDROOMS,BEDS,INSTANTBOOKABLE,REVIEWSPERMONTH,LATITUDE,LONGITUDE,PROPERTYTYPEID,ROOMTYPEID,LASTUPDATED, AmenityJoin.ACCOMMODATIONID AS ACCOMMODATIONIDJ FROM ACCOMMODATION INNER JOIN AmenityJoin ON ACCOMMODATION.ACCOMMODATIONID = AmenityJoin.ACCOMMODATIONID WHERE 1

SELECT NAME, LONGITUDE,LATITUDE, TELEPHONE, URL, AddressRegion, Activities.ACTIVITYID, ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYTYPEID, ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYID AS ACTIVITYIDJ FROM Activities INNER JOIN ActivitiesJoin ON Activities.ACTIVITYID = ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYID WHERE 1

SELECT ACTIVITYTYPE, ActivitiesTypes.ACTIVITYTYPEID, ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYTYPEID as ACTIVITYTYPEIDJ, ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYID FROM ActivitiesTypes INNER JOIN ActivitiesJoin ON ActivitiesTypes.ACTIVITYTYPEID = ActivitiesJoin.ACTIVITYTYPEID WHERE 1

SELECT AMENITYJOIN.ACCOMMODATIONID as ACCOMMODATIONID, Amenity.AMENITYID as AMENITYID, Amenity.AMENITY as AMENITY, AMENITYJOIN.AMENITYID AS AMENITYIDJ FROM AMENITY INNER JOIN AMENITYJOIN ON Amenity.AMENITYID = AMENITYJOIN.AMENITYID WHERE 1
